# MovieList — `src/store`

## Zustand + persist

- **Zustand** with **`persist`** middleware and **AsyncStorage**.
- Expose **`hydrated: boolean`**. Set **`hydrated === true`** only after rehydration completes.

## UI gate

- Watchlist **button state**, **tab badge**, and any count-driven UI must respect **`hydrated`** — do not show misleading filled/empty state before hydration.

## Watchlist item fields (normative)

```typescript
interface WatchlistItem {
  id: number;
  title: string;
  posterPath: string | null;
  voteAverage: number;
  releaseDate: string;
  genreIds: number[];
  mediaType: 'movie' | 'tv';
}
```

- Store actions: **`addItem`**, **`removeItem`**, **`isInWatchlist`**, derived **`count`** — keep signatures aligned with **`WatchlistStore`** in architecture docs.
